2014-05-21  Nicolas Léveillé  <nicolas@uucidl.com>

	* release: 0.1.4
	* integrates Travis-CI for continuous testing
	* updated tests and README.org

2014-05-20    <nicolas@uucidl.com>

	* release: 0.1.3
	* xunitgen: recorder.step(...) now allow reporting errors

2013-12-11    <nicolas@uucidl.com>

	* release: 0.1.2, 0.1.1
	* xunitgen: support encoding of xml entities and unicode
	characters, more transparent error representations

2013-12-10    <nicolas@uucidl.com>

	* release: 0.1.0
	* xunitgen:
	- shorter, better names for entry points
	- new class Recorder, recording the results of a series of steps
	- all internal timestamps in seconds
	- XunitDestination, a class marshalling the creation of xunit xml
	filenames under a root
